snippet.title: Dark Colony (1997) {VERY RARE Trailer} Real-time strategy RTS by GameTek & Strategic Simulations Inc
snippet.description:
Classic(and bloody)Real Time Strategy by Gametek with electronic music soundtrack. I have this trailer from some old magazine CD and upload it because it is rare trailer and I need help.
I like to identify soundtrack in this trailer, it's look like in final version of the game was this track not included.
If anyone know where to obtain full version of this song or name of this song, autor etc. please write it to commentaries.
Thankx.
